Package: downscalr
Type: Package
Title: Downscaling land-use change projections
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tamás Krisztin, Michael Wögerer
Maintainer: Tamás Krisztin <krisztin@iiasa.ac.at>
Description: For high-resolution projections of future land-use change IAMs often rely on downscaled projections. This package provides econometric models for prior estimation and a flexible, transparent and easy to use framework to downscale such projections. 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
